Class AbstractGenericDAO<T,K>

java.lang.Object
com.prototype.model.daos.AbstractGenericDAO<T,K>
Type Parameters:
T - the entity type handled by the DAO
K - the type of the entity's primary key
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericDAO<T,K>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BiomedicalEquipmentDAO, EntryRequestDAO, EquipmentDAO, PersonDAO, ProviderDAO, TechEquipmentDAO
public class AbstractGenericDAO<T,K> extends Object implements GenericDAO<T,K>
Generic abstract implementation of the GenericDAO interface. This class provides common CRUD operations for any entity type and serves as the base class for DAOs that require database interaction using JPA.
Version:
1.0 author Jorge Forero
